gov.fnal.ppd.dd.news

Class Channel

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.fnal.ppd.dd.news.Channel

  • public class Channel
extends java.lang.Object
    This is what an RSS news feed looks like. It has to be called "Channel" because this is what is in the RSS. Unfortunate overloading of this popular word.
    Author:
    Elliott McCrory, Fermilab AD/Instrumentation
